University who violate this policy may be subject to sanctions. See full policy (PDF):  Information and Procedural Guidelines for Pursuing and Resolving a Complaint of Discrimination, Including Sexual HarassmentPolicy owner: VP for Institutional Equity and DiversityPolicy contact:  Joanne WoodardVP for Institutional Equity and Diversity Division of Institutional Equity & Diversity940-565-2711Joanne.Woodard@unt.edu  Applies to: All UniversityDate Issued: Sunday, April 1, 2001References: Nondiscrimination/Equal Opportunity, Affirmative Action, and Non-RetaliationGrievance Voluntary Alternative Dispute Resolution SystemSexual HarassmentCross-References:    Employment of Individuals with Disabilities/Workplace Accommodations   Staff Employee Discipline and Involuntary Termination   Salary Administration (Staff)   Voluntary Alternative Dispute Resolution System   Grade Appeals    Student Complaint   Sexual Harassment   Last updated:   Date: 2011-04-01Action: Format Only     Date: 2002-08-01Action: Revision     Date: 2000-08-01Action: Revision     Date: 1999-08-01Action: Revision     Date: 1995-08-01Action: Revision    Top                          Main Menu Home FAQ Policy manual Resources Policy updates About the Policy Office  University Links  MyUNT Blackboard EagleConnect UNT Directory UNT Map UNT Calendar Jobs at UNT Give to UNT  Email & Phone   policy@unt.edu  940-565-4535    University Policy Office    Find UNT on Google Maps   1155 Union Circle #311277           Denton, Texas 76203-5017   Visitor Information  Call us Email Us UNT Map               Apply now Schedule a tour Get more info   Disclaimer | AA/EOE/ADA | Privacy | Electronic Accessibility | Required Links | UNT Home ©2017 University of North Texas Required Links         
